      "text": "The file content is too long for a single write call. Let me break it into smaller pieces and use multiple edits instead. Actually, let me write the files using a different approach - I'll write the complete files but break them up or use a bash command to write them.\n\nActually, the issue is that the content is getting truncated in my response. Let me use bash to write the files instead, using PowerShell's Set-Content.\n\nLet me think about what I need to do more carefully:\n\n1. Rewrite `score.tsx` - add Simple Mode toggle, walkthrough trigger, bigger controls, better legend\n2. Rewrite `PitchContour.tsx` - bigger fonts, better icons, accessibility\n3. Create `WalkthroughOverlay.tsx` - new component for first-time walkthrough\n\nLet me use bash/PowerShell to write these files since they're large.",
