      "type": "answer",
      "text": "All done. Refresh **http://localhost:8080/score** to see the changes.\n\n**What's new:**\n\n| Feature | Before | After |\n|---------|--------|-------|\n| **Font sizes** | 6-9px (microscopic) | 12-32px (readable) |\n| **Text size** | 28px fixed | 32px fixed |\n| **Pitch dots** | r=3 | r=5 (bigger targets) |\n| **Stress marks** | Unicode `●○·` at 7px | lucide-react `Volume2/Volume1/VolumeX` icons with labels |\n| **Coarticulation** | Unicode `→r↻ɾ` at 6px | Lucide icons in labeled badges (\"words link\", \"T->D\", \"extra sound\") |\n| **Vowel bars** | 2px height | 4px height, 30% min width |\n| **Controls** | text-xs, no icons | text-base, Play/Pause/Reset with icons |\n| **Buttons** | text-[9px] presets | text-sm presets |\n| **Legend** | 10px, no dividers | 14px, card background, dividers |\n| **Simple Mode** | none | Toggle in header -- replaces jargon with plain English |\n| **Walkthrough** | none | 6-step guided tour (auto-appears first visit, \"How to use\" button always) |\n| **Accessibility** | minimal ARIA | `role`, `aria-label`, `aria-hidden`, keyboard navigation on words, focus ring on active word |\n\n**Simple Mode labels:**\n- \"Primary stress\" -> \"Loudest word\"\n- \"Schwa\" -> \"Mumbled\"\n- \"Linking R\" -> \"Words link together\"\n- \"Flap T\" -> \"T becomes D sound\"\n- \"Compressed\" -> \"Squished vowel\"",
      "timestamp": 1781547453888
