      "text": "Now I need to create a FloatingPlayer component and add it to score.tsx. The floating player should:\n1. Be fixed in the bottom-right corner\n2. Start collapsed (just a small play/pause button)\n3. On hover, expand to show more controls (reset, WPM, annotations toggle)\n4. On idle (no mouse interaction for ~3 seconds), auto-collapse back to the minimal state\n5. Show progress indicator\n\nLet me create the component and integrate it.",
